'SHAPE SELECT' ALLOWS YOU TO SELECTSHAPES FROM EXISTING SHAPE TABLESAND   COMPILE THESE SHAPES INTO ANEW SHAPE   TABLE.AT THE PROMPT; ENTER THE NAME OF ANEXISTING SHAPE TABLE.  WHEN THE NEXTPROMPT APPEARS; ENTER A NAME FOR THENEWSHAPE TABLE.  THE SHAPE TABLEWILL THENBE LOADED; DISPLAYING EACH SHAPECONTAINED IN THE TABLE.  IF YOU WISHTO INCLUDE A SHAPE IN THE NEW SHAPETABLE; PRESS Y; IF NOT; PRESSRETURN.  AFTERALL OF THE SHAPES HAVE BEENDISPLAYED;  THE NEW TABLE WILL BECOMPILED AND      SAVED.